{"tid":1719901,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【同AGA就開到】關淑怡與撐警劉美君 兩場美加騷撻Q","createTime":"2019-11-14T07:53:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-15T09:16:54.000Z","uid":130626,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"209193b418442a21ae054190fa2c3cf1fab7c2f1","tid":1719901,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:53:47.000Z","msg":"歌手關淑怡（Shirley），早前因不滿好友黃耀明遭封殺，與大陸網民爆發罵戰，及後她棄用微博。對於逆權運動，她曾在社交網表達意見，批評官商勾結製造混亂，及譴責警方未有保護好市民。其後她的歌曲被大陸Apple Music被下架，她曾在社交網表示︰「歌星仔嚟㗎咋！做乜搞我！」<br />\n去年再簽約環球的Shirley，今日有周刊報道指，原本安排她與劉美君合作，開兩場美加演唱會，但報道指她耍大牌，與主辦商會面時，又諸多要求，最終嚇怕主辦商，不歡而散，損失了200萬收入。<br />\n不過本月2日，Shirley與後輩江海迦（AGA）到洛杉磯舉行一場演唱會，Shirley還打扮靚靚演出，事後她的社交網亦分享了演唱會的相，Shirley還表示多年沒有返美國，此行見番好多親友感到好開心。事有湊巧，早前有指劉美君因發表撐警論，而令她在新一輯的《全民造星II》被飛出局，其導師崗位由陳潔靈頂替。至於今次為何Shirley跟她開不成美加演唱會，箇中原因就不得而知。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191114/large/1573711494_59e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191114%2Flarge%2F1573711494_59e8.jpg&h=70ff7d06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191114/60265688\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191114%2F60265688&d=7CNMK8%2FfTiCK2iXV1c%2BwrJKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=4d88d18f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191114%2F60265688&h=da96eedf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191114/60265688</a>"},{"pid":"797c01f4c1eafc6071597b793a037952d36548ef","tid":1719901,"uid":245552,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T07:56:33.000Z","msg":"撐警撐到變過街老鼠<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵撚死呀老鼠君</span>"},{"pid":"408a1098adf81096fd5566f6041a7e624b3bd732","tid":1719901,"uid":3976,"like":11,"dislike":